18#ifndef _LVM_TEXT_EXPORT_H
19#define _LVM_TEXT_EXPORT_H
20
21#define outf(args...) do {if (!out_text(args)) return_0;} while (0)
22#define outnl(f) do {if (!out_newline(f)) return_0;} while (0)
23
24struct formatter;
25struct lv_segment;
26struct config_node;
27
28int out_size(struct formatter *f, uint64_t size, const char *fmt, ...)
29 __attribute__ ((format(printf, 3, 4)));
30
31int out_hint(struct formatter *f, const char *fmt, ...)
32 __attribute__ ((format(printf, 2, 3)));
33
34int out_text(struct formatter *f, const char *fmt, ...)
35 __attribute__ ((format(printf, 2, 3)));
36
37int out_config_node(struct formatter *f, const struct config_node *cn);
38
39int out_areas(struct formatter *f, const struct lv_segment *seg,
40 const char *type);
41
42void out_inc_indent(struct formatter *f);
43void out_dec_indent(struct formatter *f);
44int out_newline(struct formatter *f);
45
46#endif
